SUMMARY:Magic Academy: Learn to Play @ Top Deck Games - Cherry Hill
LOCATION:Top Deck Games - Cherry Hill\, 1400 Haddonfield-Berlin Road\, Che
 rry Hill Township\, New Jersey\, 08003
DESCRIPTION:Format: New Player Event\nCost: $10\nStore: https://www.topdec
 kgamesonline.com/\nDetails: https://locator.wizards.com/events/10893386\n\
 n🎓 Enroll & Learn the Arcane: New to Magic? Consider this your first da
 y of class. Our knowledgeable “professors” will guide you through the 
 fundamentals so you can start casting spells with confidence.\n✨ Find Yo
 ur College\, Find Your Crew: Whether you’re a seasoned mage or a first-y
 ear student\, there’s a place for you here. Forge friendships\, share st
 rategies\, and discover where you belong.\nAll skill levels welcome\n\nENT
 RY: $10\n- Pack of a recent Magic set\n\nFORMAT: Learn to Play\n- Introduc
 tion to basics\, cards\, rules\, and terms\n- Guided Play. Players will re
 ceive their own pre-built Welcome Deck or Beginner Boxes and paired with o
 thers to play friendly practice games with guidance from staff and experie
 nced players\n\n- Each participant will receive a promo card and a welcome
  deck\n- Each Welcome Deck contains one randomly inserted reward that gran
 ts either a physical reward or a digital MTG Arena reward\n- Please presen
 t the reward insert to a store employee to redeem it\nSource: wizards-loca
 tor
URL;VALUE=URI:https://locator.wizards.com/events/10893386
END:VEVENT
